{"title":"迎春曲","authors":["温承训"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":1,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京第三机床厂　温承训"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难接着困难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超额接着超额"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在困难和超额的变换中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年转瞬而过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻想着什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻充满着欢乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这年终岁末"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在马丁炉旁放歌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"固执的大雁结队南飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在找寻温暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懒惰的虫儿土里冬眠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在躲避风寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁人对你们羡慕？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁人对你们伤感？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里也不去呀一刻也不闲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春暖花开紧接着花开春暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们迎接祖国第二个春天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林海、油泉、煤田、铀矿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你又能储藏几许能量？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党勘测了六万万座心房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它蕴藏着无限高贵的理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年计划就是开发它的计划"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用它不竭不尽的力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀起钢水的巨浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让高炉像火山爆发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂喷着铁浆……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“十五年后赶上英国”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像春雷在山谷里轰响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面八方传来回声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“赶得上——赶得上！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看西方："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那“国旗不落日”的国家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只剩下落日的残照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暮色苍茫晚景凄凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！啊！东方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从长江、从鞍钢、从每一座农场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正射出万道霞光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如霜枫、如榴火、如琥珀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"簇拥着初升的朝阳！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}